==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lechery
<hw>Lech"er*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>lecherie</ets>, OF. <ets>lecherie</ets>. See
<er>Lecher</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Free indulgence of lust;
excessive indulgence in sexual relations; -- used mostly of
men.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Selfish pleasure; delight.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Massinger.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lecithin</ent>⟦br⟧
